data.description: Have you seen the shop? The outdoor gas firepit? The pad built for a hot tub? The large lot? Imagine the indoor and outdoor memories. This beautiful home was built in 2019 with 1,962sqft, 3bed, 2bath, 2 car garage on 0.39 acre with a 1,200 sqft detached shop. The colors in this home work perfectly together. Flooring includes LVP and carpet. A fourth bedroom was sacrificed to make a large pantry and a walk in closet for the 2nd bedroom. Plenty of space with an open concept for the kitchen, dining and living areas. The memories made here will be perfect. Enjoy the space that this large lot offers even with the 1,200 sqft detached shop. Shop has electricity, a bathroom, Bluetooth speakers, is insulated, with a 14 foot tall door. Oh the possibilities. Close to city park. A must buy now.
